title: [Week 8] LP Forest Rewards
body:
What should be done for Week 8 of LP Forest rewards?

Do nothing - keep current setup (2.25T/week to 6 LP Forests total)

Double rewards for KuSwap LPs to 1T/week each for 3 LPs (3.75T/week for 6 LP Forests total)

Double rewards for KoffeeSwap LPs to 500B/week each for 3 LPs (3T/week for 6 LP Forests total)

Expand to new AMM with 250B/week each for 3 LPs (3T/week for 9 LP Forests total)
